| `RAILWAY_PRODUCTION_SERVICE_ID` | Railway → production service → Settings |
| `RAILWAY_PRODUCTION_ENVIRONMENT_ID` | Railway → production environment URL |
| `RAILWAY_STAGING_URL` | Staging public URL |
| `RAILWAY_PRODUCTION_URL` | Production public URL |

